  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA41">
<l>orupā lulakaḷanta mālavaṉā maṟṟai</l>
<l>yorupā lumaiyavaḷā meṉṟā - lirupālu</l>
<l>niṉṉuruva māka niṟanteriya māṭṭōmā</l>
<l>ṉiṉṉuruvō miṉṉuruvō nērntu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If one says in one part he is Māl who measured</l>
<l>the world, in another part she is Umā,</l>
<l>as your form is both parts, we cannot be clear about the colour.</l>
<l>Is it properly your form/colour or is it the form/colour of lightning?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
